episodes.title: Scientology is Suprisingly Mental
episodes.description:
This is my thirteenth video.
Today, we are dunking on Scientology. Focusing on the life of L Ron Hubbard, aliens and other utterly mental stuff. It is really quite astonishing that Scientology has been so successful, given that it is based on absolute nonsense made up by a mentally ill science fiction writer. Anyway, I hope you enjoy the video.
For those of you begging for videos on other religions, such as Buddhism, Jainism, Judaism, Christianity and Islam - please have patience. All ideologies will be treated to equal levels of mockery in time. Be sure to subscribe so you don't miss your favourite.
As for the upload schedule, it has gone to shit.
All is lost.
If I am to complete the twelve promised videos of 2025, I must now make four videos in the next two months.
Considering that this video alone took me as much time, the odds of keeping my word are low.
But I really hate going back on my promises, so if any of you have a miracle up your arse that you could pull out and lend me, I would appreciate it.
